          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              I built <strong>real portfolio sites</strong> across 3 AI builders. Not demo sites—actual portfolios I'd show to clients.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed ml-6 list-disc">
